description: AMUNDI MSCI WORLD UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI World Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to large and mid-cap companies in developed countries, with a single transaction. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi MSCI World UCITS ETF - USD (C)
